Package: NullstrapDE
Type: Package
Title: NullstrapDE add-on of DESeq2 and edgeR for FDR Calibration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chenxin", "Jiang", 
           email = "cflorajiang@ucla.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Implements the NullstrapDE synthetic-null-data-based calibration framework for 
    differential expression analysis. Provides NullstrapDE-enabled versions 
    of DESeq2 and edgeR that produce more accurate FDR control by 
    simulating null distributions directly from fitted model parameters. 
    Functions include Nullstrap_DESeq2 and Nullstrap_edgeR, which wrap 
    standard workflows while applying the NullstrapDE thresholding step.
